songs.title: Twin
songs.lyrics:
(A-ha ha!)
[Verse 1]
Your warmth, your warmth is so deep
Your gaze beams a hole into me

[Chorus 1]
Controlling again
Unseparated twins
Controlling again

[Verse 2]
You've sucked all the breath out of me
You'll squeeze all the life out of me

[Chorus 1]
Controlling again
Unseparated twins
Controlling again

[Chorus 2]
Controlling again
Unseparated twins
You might have been

[Outro]
Come gentle, slowly
Down tonight
